children.description: Peace has settled on Earth, and unfortunately for Goku, that means getting a job! But a generous gift may change that. Meanwhile, Trunks and Goten seek a pre-wedding gift for Videl. It’s all fun and games for now, but danger lurks in the galaxy.
children.title: The Peace Reward - Who Will Get the 100 Million Zeni?

children.description: While Goku gets to spend his time training on King Kai’s planet, Vegeta is on a family vacation! But this brooding prince would rather spend his time getting stronger than on bonding. Elsewhere, Beerus and Whis continue their path of destruction.
children.title: To the Promised Resort! Vegeta Goes on a Family Trip?!

children.description: Beerus works to find the unbeatable foe in his dream while Supreme Kai tries to keep information about Beerus from Goku. Unfortunately, Beerus is already planning to visit the Saiyan and test his strength.
children.title: Where's the Rest of the Dream?! In Search of the Super Saiyan God!

children.description: Bulma’s birthday bash has begun! While everyone enjoys the party, Trunks and Goten snoop around the prizes for the bingo tournament. All seven Dragon Balls await the winner but also attract familiar foes—the Pilaf gang!
children.title: Aim for the Dragon Balls! Pilaf Gang in Action!

children.description: Goku faces off against Beerus in a hard-hitting battle despite King Kai’s best efforts to keep them separate. But is Goku’s strongest form enough to take on the God of Destruction? On Earth, Vegeta surprises Bulma by showing up for her party!
children.title: The Ultimate Fight on King Kai's Planet! Goku Vs the God of Destruction Beerus

children.description: An uninvited guest appears at Bulma’s party! Beerus crashes the party and Vegeta is stunned after memories of the God’s visit to his home planet plague him. He does the only thing he can—ensure Beerus has a good time at the party!
children.title: Don't Anger the God of Destruction! Excitement at the Birthday Party

children.description: When even Buu can’t land a hit on Beerus, Vegeta steps in to calm the angry God. The other Z fighters step in, but Beerus proves to be a challenge unlike any other. But when he threatens Bulma, will Vegeta finally make his move?
children.title: How Dare You Hurt My Bulma! Vegeta's Sudden, Angry Shift?!

children.description: With a new surge of power, Vegeta attacks Beerus! But it isn’t enough. Giving Earth a second chance, Beerus challenges Oolong to rock-paper-scissors. Will Goku arrive in time to help his friends and planet?
children.title: Goku Arrives! A Last Chance from Beerus Sama?!

children.description: Summoning Shenron, they learn what the Super Saiyan God is. Rather than a particular person, it is a kindhearted Saiyan who can become one. But transforming into one requires more Saiyans than they have on board—until Videl reveals a surprise!
children.title: Sorry for the Wait, Beerus Sama. The Super Saiyan God Is Finally Born!

children.description: With the powers of a Super Saiyan God, Goku faces Beerus! Or, well he tries to. The immense power of a God takes a little getting used to but the longer he fights, the more Goku proves he’s a real challenge. The true battle begins!
children.title: Unleash It, Goku! The Power of the Super Saiyan God!!

children.description: With his powers mostly under control, Goku ramps up the battle. But Beerus is still filled with unbelievable power and Goku takes hit after hit. Even though his injuries heal, can he handle the true strength of Beerus’ power?
children.title: Let’s Keep Going, Lord Beerus! The Battle of Gods!

children.description: The battle between gods continues to rage on, but their powers are starting to affect the universe. With each blow they exchange, the universe crumbles around them. Will the battle end before the universe does?!
children.title: The Universe Crumbles?! Clash! God of Destruction Vs. Super Saiyan God

children.description: Goku continues to surprise Beerus with his growing powers. As their fight escalates, the universe manages to stay intact, but for how long? Then, Goku reverts back to a Super Saiyan! Have his godly powers run out?
children.title: Goku, Surpass the Super Saiyan God!

children.description: Goku continues the hard fought battle, but his powers still aren’t enough to take down the God of Destruction. When his energy finally runs out, Earth’s fate is sealed! Or is it? The battle of the gods reaches its end!
children.title: This Is Every Ounce of Power I Have! The Battle of Gods' Conclusion!

children.description: With Beerus gone and the world at peace once more, the Z Fighters resume their normal lives. But nothing ever remains calm, as aliens arrive on Earth to thank and challenge the hero who fought Beerus. And that hero is…Mr. Satan?!
children.title: Make a Miracle, Satan the Hero! A Challenge from Outer Space

children.description: When Vegeta finds Whis having lunch with Bulma, he demands he be taken to Beerus. But when Whis reveals he’s actually the god’s teacher, the stubborn Saiyan prince is willing to beg to become his student. But at what cost?
children.title: Vegeta Becomes an Apprentice?! Winning Whis Over!

children.description: Gohan’s precious daughter is born, and Chichi refuses to let her become a martial artist. Luckily, Bulma manages to talk some sense into her but also reveals where Vegeta has been training, leaving Goku desperate to find a way to join them.
children.title: Pan Is Born! And Goku Goes on a Training Trip?!

children.description: Goku arrives on Beerus’ planet to start training only to find that Vegeta is doing more housework than training! But when he realizes just how strong the other has grown, he’s ready to do whatever it takes. As they train, a new danger grows.
children.title: I'm Here, Too! Training Begins on Beerus' Planet!

children.description: The remaining members of the Frieza Force have slowly been gathering to seek revenge for their fallen leader. While Goku and Vegeta train, Sorbet and his men head to Earth in search of the Dragon Balls and a way to bring back Frieza!
children.title: Despair Rises! The Emperor of Evil, Frieza, Resurrected!

children.description: Frieza plans his revenge against Goku and Earth, but when he learns how strong Goku has become, he begins training. After four months, he’s finally ready to attack, and only the warning of his arrival from a new ally can prepare our heroes!
children.title: Jaco's Warning! Frieza and His 1000 Troops Approach

children.description: Without any way to get a hold of Goku or Vegeta, only Gohan and the remaining Z fighters are ready to face Frieza. Up against 1000 troops and the emperor of evil, our heroes may face more of a challenge than expected!
children.title: The Start of Revenge! the Malice of Frieza Army Strikes Gohan!

children.description: Tagoma proves to be a tough opponent and even Piccolo can’t take him. Gotenks joins the battle but suddenly Tagoma is taken over by…Ginyu?! Gohan is able to face him as a Super Saiyan but can he keep up when Frieza makes his move?
children.title: Change! an Unexpected Return! His Name Is Ginyu!!

children.description: Piccolo falls after attempting to save Gohan but there’s no time to deal with the loss. While Bulma finally gets a message to Whis for Goku and Vegeta, Gohan powers up to his highest level. And so does Freiza. Will Goku make it in time?
children.title: The Earth! Gohan! Absolute Peril! Hurry and Get Here, Son Goku!!

children.description: Goku and Frieza finally face off! With their powers matched, Frieza begins attacking Goku’s friends to catch him off guard. Frustrated, Vegeta pushes him to give it his all and face Frieza in his ultimate form!
children.title: Clash! Frieza Vs Son Goku - This Is The Result of My Training!

children.description: Not to be outdone by Goku’s new form, Frieza reveals a new one of his own. Once again the two face off in an evenly matched battle. Meanwhile, Beerus and Whis make their way to Earth but run into allies of their own.
children.title: An All-Out Battle! The Revenge of Golden Frieza

children.description: Goku is having trouble facing Golden Frieza until he realizes the other is quickly losing stamina. Gaining the upper hand, Goku gives Frieza a chance to leave Earth for good. But the emperor of evil isn’t ready to give up his revenge just yet.
children.title: A Glint of Hope Shines Through in a Crisis! Time to Fight Back, Son Goku!

children.description: With Goku badly injured, Vegeta steps in to face Frieza. Stronger than ever, Vegeta proves to be a challenge and an enraged Frieza destroys the planet! Protected by Whis, the Z fighters are given a chance to save Earth, if they act fast enough.
children.title: The Earth Explodes?! The Deciding Kamehameha

children.description: Vegeta and Goku are continuing their training under Whis when they receive a pair of visitors—Beerus’ brother and Whis’ sister! After a comparison of culinary delights, Champa challenges Beerus to a universe-versus-universe tournament.
children.title: The God of Destruction from Universe 6 - His Name Is Champa

children.description: Bulma suggests summoning Shenron to find the remaining Super Dragon Balls, but even his power is not enough. As they prepare for the upcoming match, Beerus reveals there’s a fighter stronger than Goku who’s going to join the team of the 7th Universe!
children.title: The Martial Arts Match Has Been Decided! The Team Captain Is Stronger Than Goku

children.description: Goku and Vegeta must find two more members for the tournament—but who will be worthy to face the 6th Universe alongside Goku and Vegeta? Gohan? Piccolo? Or even...Majin Buu?! But first, a review of what the heck is really going on!
children.title: A Review Before the 'Martial Arts Match' - Who Are the Last Two Members?!

children.description: To find out more about the Super Dragon Balls, Jaco takes Bulma to the all-knowing alien, Master Zuno. But their trip is disturbed when they encounter the criminal, Geppuman. They’re given three questions to ask Zuno—will they get the answers they need?
children.title: Off to Zuno Sama's! Find Out Where Super Dragon Balls Are!

children.description: It’s time to head to the tournament! Everyone gathers, and the mysterious fighter Monaka is finally revealed. Once on the “Planet With No Name,” they size up their competition which includes…another Saiyan?! Are they ready for the ultimate tournament?
children.title: The Match Begins! Let's All Go to the Nameless Planet!

children.description: Goku faces the first fighter of the 6th Universe—Botamo. Things don’t look good at the start when Goku struggles from overeating, but it’s nothing a little stretching can’t fix. Next, he’s up against the 6th Universe’s very own Frieza-like warrior—Frost!
children.title: Behold, Universe 6! This Is the Super Saiyan? Son Goku!

children.description: After Goku’s sudden defeat, Piccolo steps into the ring! Frost continues to be a challenge, and right when Piccolo is beaten, Jaco makes a discovery—Frost hasn’t been fighting fair! But Vegeta’s not ready to let him off with a disqualification.
children.title: Piccolo Vs. Frost - Put It All on the Special Beam Cannon!

children.description: Vegeta prepares to face Frost, who has no intention of discontinuing his cheating. But with a single hit, Vegeta knocks Frost completely out of the ring for the win. Before the next round, Goku is added back to the lineup, and Champa adds a new rule.
children.title: Turn Rage into Strength! Vegeta's Full-On Battle

children.description: The battle literally heats up as Magetta starts a heatwave. Cornered, Vegeta destroys the barrier around him and unleashes his power against his opponent. Will he bring this battle to a cool conclusion or melt under pressure?
children.title: An Unexpected Desperate Battle! Vegeta's Furious Explosion!

children.description: It’s Saiyan versus Saiyan in this next epic battle! The two seem evenly matched until Vegeta demands Cabbe transform into a Super Saiyan, only to learn the boy is incapable. Will Vegeta show mercy, or has he strayed to his old, evil ways?!
children.title: Don't Forget Your Saiyan Pride! Vegeta Vs the Saiyan of Universe 6

children.description: Vegeta goes up against the last member of the 6th Universe, the assassin Hit! With movements so fast nobody can even see him, Hit proves to be a true match for Vegeta. Will the prince of Saiyans finally fall?
children.title: The Ultimate Warrior of Universe 6! Assassin Hit Appears!!

children.description: Figuring out Hit’s “time-skipping” ability allows Goku to keep up—until Hit powers up! Will Goku finally face defeat, or does the Saiyan have a secret power of his own?
children.title: The Advanced 'Time-Skip' Fights Back?! Will It Come Forth? Goku's New Technique!

children.description: Goku and Hit continue to fight evenly matched as they reach unbelievable heights with their abilities. But as Goku continues to strain his body—he does the unthinkable! Will the 6th Universe be named the winners?!
children.title: At Last, It Comes to an End! Is the Winner Beerus? Or is it Champa?

children.description: Before the winner can gloat, a newcomer appears in the ring! Beerus and Champa are struck with fear—just who is this Zeno? And finally, it’s time to make a wish on the Super Dragon Balls, that is, if they can find the last one.
children.title: Come, God of Dragons - And Pretty Please Grant My Wish!

children.description: Bulma plans a victory party for all the fighters and wants to include Monaka. Beerus fears Goku will learn the truth of his newest rival and tries to keep him from going. But when Monaka shows up, they’ll have to figure out a way to keep it all secret!
children.title: Trouble at the Victory Celebration! Showdown at Last?! Monaka vs. Son Goku

children.description: Goku starts having trouble controlling his body and energy! After visiting with King Kai, he learns he’s on strict bed rest until his energy levels out. But when he goes to stay at Gohan’s, he finds taking it easy with baby Pan around isn’t so easy.
children.title: Goku's "Ki" is Out of Control?! Looking After Pan is A Lot of Trouble

children.description: After getting stuck in Monaka’s truck, Goten and Trunks wind up on Planet Pot-au-feu. Here, they protect an old man and get caught in a fight over…water?! But the truth about this water could leave them high and dry!
children.title: Seal of Planet Potofu - Secret of the Superhuman Water is Unleashed

children.description: After being drained of his energy, Vegeta and the others escape and learn more about the Superhuman Water. And if they don’t stop the clones, Vegeta could disappear—for good! With time running out, will Gotenks be enough to stop them?
children.title: Vegeta Disappears?! The Threat of Duplicated Vegeta!

children.description: As Vegeta begins to disappear, Goku faces the duplicate Vegeta! But can he defeat the copy and save the original before he vanishes? And when the fight starts, is Vegeta rooting for…his clone?!
children.title: Goku vs. Duplicated Vegeta! Who's Gonna Win?!

children.description: Life in the present may be peaceful but trouble is stirring in the future! Trunks is risking everything to get back to the past to find help. But will he escape the new evil that threatens the future in time to get help from our heroes?
children.title: An SOS from the Future! A Dark New Enemy Emerges!!

children.description: With barely enough time to stop the dark entity that’s after him, Trunks travels back to the past. But when he arrives, can present Trunks handle seeing his future self?!
children.title: Hope!! Once More Awaken in the Present, Trunks

children.description: After regaining consciousness, Future Trunks describes how he came to arrive in the present. But apparently not even the gods are allowed to meddle with the past. Bulma and Future Trunks might have a bit of explaining to do.
children.title: A Message from the Future - Goku Black Strikes!

children.description: Black suddenly appears from a mysterious portal. Goku sees this as an opportunity to test his look-alike’s power firsthand. But while the battle rages on, Black glances at the time machine with a sinister look in his eye.
children.title: Goku Vs Black! The Closed Path to the Future

children.description: Bulma gets to work repairing the old time machine that she’s kept. Meanwhile, Future Trunks recalls his experiences with Mai. But two questions remain: why does Black have a time ring? And what’s the extent of his power?
children.title: Feelings That Travel Beyond Time - Trunks and Mai

children.description: Repairs on the time machine continue, so Future Trunks goes to visit an old friend. However, times have changed, and the reunion isn’t quite what he expected.
children.title: Teacher and Student Reunited - Son Gohan and "Future" Trunks

children.description: The nature of Black’s power remains a mystery, so Whis, Beerus, and Goku go to the 10th Universe to find answers. Will challenging an apprentice Supreme Kai really help with the investigation? Goku seems to think so.
children.title: Uncover Black's Identity! To the Sacred World of the Kais!

children.description: The time machine repairs are finishing up. Vegeta and Future Trunks go training, but the extent of Vegeta’s power is unlike anything Future Trunks has ever seen.
children.title: The One Who Inherits the Saiyan Blood - Trunk's Resolve
I Want to See Son Goku - Zen‐Oh Sama's Summoning!

children.description: Future Trunks, Vegeta, and Goku finally use the time machine with intention to confront Black. But when they arrive, they’re greeted by a familiar face and an unfamiliar power. Will they be able to stand up to this new threat?
children.title: Rematch With Goku Black! Super Saiyan Rosé Appears

children.description: With Vegeta out of the fight, Goku and Future Trunks must fight Future Zamasu and Black with a man down. But can they hope to defeat an opponent who brushes off even the strongest attacks?
children.title: The God With the Immortal Body - Zamasu Descends
Zamasu and Black - The Mystery of the Two Deepens

children.description: Supreme Kai Gowasu is in grave danger! Now that gods are involved, Zamasu’s treachery isn’t a mortal matter anymore. Beerus will have to take matters into his own hands.
children.title: Protect Supreme Kai Gowasu - Destroy Zamasu!

children.description: Beerus is convinced that his actions should’ve influenced the future, but Future Trunks isn’t so sure! Now it’s time for Goku, Vegeta, and Future Trunks to see for themselves—and Bulma is going, too!
children.title: Back to the Future - Goku Black's Identity Is Revealed!!

children.description: The future is unchanged, Black isn’t what Goku had initially thought, and the situation has escalated to something more severe. With this new information, will the Saiyan trio fare better than before?
children.title: Zamasu's Ambition - The Awful "Zero Mortal Plan" Is Revealed

children.description: Fighting rages on, and things are looking grim for our heroes. They might not be able to win, but Future Trunks can at least defend the others while they escape! Time is running out, but a new strategy may be the key to victory.
children.title: I'll Protect the World! Trunks' Furious Super Power Explodes!!
Don't Disrespect Saiyan Cells! Vegeta's Heroic Battle Begins!!
Revere Him! Praise Him! Fusion Zamasu's Explosive Birth!!
Is This the Final Judgement?! The Ultimate Power of the Absolute God
The Climactic Battle! The Miraculous Power of a Relentless Warrior!
With New Hope!! In Our Hearts- Farewell, Trunks
Come Forth, Shenron! Whose Wish Will be Granted?!
Goku Vs Arale! A Ridiculous Battle Will End The Earth?!
Champa's Challenge! This Time We Fight With Baseball!
The Death of Goku! The Guaranteed Assassination Mission
Will There Be A Counterattack?! The Invisible Killing Strike!!
Gohan's Misfortune! An Unexpected Great Saiyaman Movie?!
For the Ones He Loves! The Unbeatable Great Saiyaman!!
Goku and Krillin Back to the Old Training Grounds
Defeat These Terrifying Enemies! Krillin's Fighting Spirit Returns!
Let's Do It, Zen-Oh Sama! The All-Universe Martial Arts Tournament!!
The Gods of Every Universe In Shock?! Losers Erased In The Tournament Of Power
Universe 9's Basil The Kicker VS Universe 7's Majin Buu!!
Awaken Your Sleeping Battle Spirit! Son Gohan's Fight!!
Bergamo The Crusher VS Son Goku! Which One Wields The Limtless Power?!
Never Forgive Son Goku! Toppo The Warrior Of Justice Intrudes!!
Form the Universe 7 Representing Team! Who are the Strongest Ten?!
Son Goku The Recruiter Invites Krillin And No. 18
The Universes Begin To Make Their Moves Their Individual Motives
Fists Cross For The First Time! Android #17 Vs Son Goku!!
Hunt The Poachers! Goku And No. 17's United Front!!
Gohan And Piccolo Teacher And Pupil Clash In Max Training!
An Unkown Beauty Appears! The Tenshin-style Dojo's Mystery?!
See The Wall That Must Be Passed! Goku Vs Gohan
Which Universe Will Survive?! The Strongest Warriors Are Gathering!!
Emergency Development! The Incomplete Ten Members!!
You're The Tenth Warrior! Goku Goes To See Frieza!!
The Emperor of Evil Returns! A Reception of Mysterious Assassins?!
The Worst! The Most Evil! Frieza's Rampage!!
The Time Is Here! To The World Of Void For The Fate Of The Universe!!
Survive! The Tournament Of Power Begins At Last!!
Oh, Uncertainty! A Universe Despairs!!
Show Them! Krillin's True Power!!
Out Of Control! The Savage Berserker Awakens!!
The Impending Warriors of Justice! The Pride Troopers!!
The Power of Love Explodes?! Universe 2's Little Witch Warriors!!
Gohan, Show No Mercy! Showdown With Universe 10!!
The Ultimate High Speed Battle Begins! Goku and Hit Join Forces!!
A Desperate Battle! Master Roshi's Sacrifice!!
Find Him! Death Match With An Invisible Attacker!!
Revenge "F"! The Cunning Trap?!
Frieza And Frost! Conjoined Malice?!
This Is The Universe's Ultimate Battle! Son Goku VS Jiren!!
The Surreal Supreme Battle! Hit vs Jiren!!
A Saiyan's Vow! Vegeta's Resolution!!
With Great Joy! The Repeat Battle-Crazy Saiyan Fight!!
Intimidating Passion! The Birth of a New Super Warrior!!
Goku vs Kefla! Super Saiyan Blue Defeated?!
The Sign of a Comeback! Ultra Instinct's Huge Explosion!!
Showdown of Love! Androids vs Universe 2!!
Accelerated Tragedy - Vanishing Universes…
Unavoidable?! The Fierce Stealth Attack!!
The Perfect Survival Tactic! Universe 3's Menacing Assassin!!
All-Out War! The Ultimate Quadruple Merge vs Universe 7's Full-Scale Attack!!
For One's Own Pride! Vegeta's Challenge to be the Strongest!!
Body and Soul, Full Power Release! Goku and Vegeta!!
The Fiercely Overwhelming Assault! Gohan's Last Stand!!
With Imposing Presence! God of Destruction Toppo Descends!!
Surpass Even a God! Vegeta's Desperate Blow!!
The Approaching Wall! The Final Barrier of Hope!!
Noble Pride to the End! Vegeta Falls!!
Limits Super Surpassed! Ultra Instinct Mastered!!
The Greatest Showdown of All Time! The Ultimate Survival Battle!!
The Miraculous Conclusion! Farewell, Goku! Until We Meet Again!!
